OL,3,CChannel Islands break temperature
OL,4,Crecords as Jersey exceeds 39C
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey have broken their
OL,7,Fall-time temperature records as the
OL,8,FChannel Islands swelter in extreme
OL,9,Fheat.
OL,11,FJersey has surpassed 39C for the
OL,12,Ffirst time, beating the previous high
OL,13,Fof 37.9C - set in July 2022.
OL,15,FGuernsey is slightly cooler but has
OL,16,Fstill hit its hottest-ever day with
OL,17,F36.4C so far - smashing the previous
OL,18,Frecord of 34.3C, set in August 2003,
OL,19,Fby more than two degrees.
OL,26,@lD@]OXsD@XOXuD@HOXyD@EOXzD@OOX
