OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1782730080
OL,3,CChannel Islands break temperature
OL,4,Crecords as Jersey exceeds 39C
OL,6,FA thunderstorm is forecasted later on
OL,7,FThursday, which will help to dampen
OL,8,Fdown the heat.
OL,10,FThese latest figures mean Jersey has
OL,11,Fexperienced its first, third, and
OL,12,Fsixth hottest days ever this week.
OL,14,FThe all-time highest temperature for
OL,15,Fthe British Isles is 40.3C - recorded
OL,16,Fin Coningsby, Lincolnshire, on 19 July
OL,17,F2022.
OL,19,FProvisional highest temperatures:
OL,26,@lD@]OXwD@ZOX
