OL,3,CChannel Islands break temperature
OL,4,Crecords as Jersey exceeds 39C
OL,6,FAll data provided by Jersey and
OL,7,FGuernsey Met
OL,9,FMany schools have closed early, with
OL,10,Fsome shutting entirely as classrooms
OL,11,Fbecame too hot to teach safely.
OL,13,FJersey's General Hospital has
OL,14,Fcancelled 34 non-urgent surgeries due
OL,15,Fto high temperatures in two operating
OL,16,Ftheatres, but emergency and maternity
OL,17,Fcare are unaffected.
OL,26,@lD@]OX
