FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1782730080
OL,3,CChannel Islands break temperature
OL,4,Crecords as Jersey exceeds 39C
OL,6,FIt is the second time in a month that
OL,7,Fprocedures have been disrupted by hot
OL,8,Fweather, with more than 80 cancelled
OL,9,Fat the end of May after an air
OL,10,Fconditioning fault.
OL,12,FSimon West, Medical Director for
OL,13,FHealth and Care Jersey, says: "This
OL,14,Fissue does not relate to the new
OL,15,Fchiller water unit, which was
OL,16,Finstalled earlier this month, but
OL,17,Fanother chiller unit.
OL,19,F"I'd like to thank our estates team,
OL,20,Fwho have been working around the clock
OL,21,Fto try to resolve the issue.
OL,26,@lD@]OX
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
