PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1782730080
OL,3,CChannel Islands break temperature
OL,4,Crecords as Jersey exceeds 39C
OL,6,F"Once again, the high temperatures
OL,7,Fhave highlighted the challenges of
OL,8,Fworking in an older facility."
OL,10,FHe adds that affected patients have
OL,11,Fbeen contacted and the process of
OL,12,Frebooking postponed procedures is
OL,13,Falready underway.
OL,26,@lD@]OX
